tv.amwa.maj.industry

Class StrongReferenceSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • tv.amwa.maj.industry.StrongReferenceSet

  • public class StrongReferenceSet
extends Object

    Utilities for manipulating media entities stored in a strong reference set. These static methods ensure a consistent approach to managing elements of a set through add, remove and contains operations.

    See Also:
    StrongReferenceVector, WeakReferenceSet, TypeDefinitionSet, TypeDefinitionStrongObjectReference
